object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
select distinct 
cb.batch_id,
metal_dr.source_name,
metal_dr.load_type,
metal_dr.system_id,          
metal_dr.parent_id,          
metal_dr.cmm_container,      
metal_dr.id,     
metal_dr.update_count,       
metal_dr.update_user,        
metal_dr.update_timestamp,   
metal_dr.template_id_ref,     
metal_dr.type_cd,            
metal_dr.source_cd,          
metal_dr.status_cd,          
metal_dr.result_cd,          
metal_dr.request_type_cd,     
metal_dr.transmitted_dt,     
metal_dr.transmitted_tm,     
metal_dr.received_dt,        
metal_dr.received_tm,        
metal_dr.processed_dt,       
metal_dr.processed_tm,       
metal_dr.add_dt,             
metal_dr.add_tm,             
metal_dr.party_id,           
metal_dr.row_id,             
metal_dr.state_specific_code, 
metal_dr.inspection_number,  
metal_dr.inspection_id,
bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_id,
bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_md5checksum
FROM $$raw_schema.acx_data_report metal_dr
LEFT JOIN $$staging_schema.acx_data_report bronze_dr
    ON CAST(TRIM(metal_dr.system_id) AS INT) = CAST(bronze_dr.system_id AS INT)
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(metal_dr.cmm_container), '') = COALESCE(bronze_dr.cmm_container, '')
   AND bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
   AND bronze_dr.acx_data_report_row_status = 'Active'
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
ORDER BY 
    metal_dr.system_id,
    metal_dr.cmm_container,
    metal_dr.id;

'template_id_ref' || template_id_ref ||
'type_cd' || type_cd ||
'source_cd' || source_cd ||

'result_cd' || result_cd ||
'request_type_cd' || request_type_cd ||
'transmitted_dt' || transmitted_dt ||
'transmitted_tm' || transmitted_tm ||
'received_dt' || received_dt ||
'received_tm' || received_tm ||
'processed_dt' || processed_dt ||
'processed_tm' || processed_tm ||
'add_dt' || add_dt ||
'add_tm' || add_tm ||
'party_id' || party_id ||
'state_specific_code' || state_specific_code ||
'inspection_number' || inspection_number ||
'inspection_id' || inspection_id)
